value.0: Strange runes and pictographs, likely arcane in nature, have been scorched into the sides of this hide-covered strongbox.

Somehow the molten form of the Ancient Obsidian Elemental which you scooped this substance from, has allowed the obsidian to maintain a semi-liquid form, not unlike mercury.

What you might be able to do with it, is anyone's guess...
